Whitney Nico Whitney.Nico@uss.salvationarmy.org;Zimmerman, Keith Keith.Zimmerman@austintexas.govGood evening all,Registration at the Central Library forCold Weather Sheltersis getting underway. People can useCap Metro services to ride, and no one will be denied transportation to theirdestination due to lack of fare for the duration of the cold weather event. Once at the Central Library free transportation will be provided to an overnight shelter.Kindly,-Lara
